snippet.textDisplay:
LBJ saying we don’t need these games to know where they are? Well you can say that if you’ve played perfect ball, but there are still lots of holes in the teams game that need help and consistency. To name three:
Bench scoring - Jamal Crawford
Three point scoring - JR Smith
Consistent wing defenders - Jonathan Simmons
Clippers are also picking up Joikim Noah to continue to bring support for Kawhi since he’s never really carried a team like LBJ.
Noah is so they have a guy at the rim to try and take away LBJ’s driving game.
I think if he Lakers are serious about winning it all this year, don’t be outdone by Jerry West in bringing all the support you can for your star. Jerry West has brought in every possible support to insure they win. Lakers should pickup the three I mentioned above to make them overwhelming favorites.
